# Concourse

[Concourse](https://concourse-ci.org/) is our CI/CD tool. It can be accessed by proxying into the Kubernetes cluster.

An overview of the pipelines currently used can be found [here](https://github.com/cabinetoffice/national-leadership-centre-deployment/tree/master/pipelines).

To quickly connect to concourse use the following:

```
export POD_NAME=$(kubectl get pods --namespace concourse -l "app=concourse-web" -o jsonpath="{.items[0].metadata.name}")
kubectl port-forward --namespace concourse $POD_NAME 8080:8080
```

Concourse should be available at [http://127.0.0.1:8080](http://127.0.0.1:8080).